{"type": "article", "id": 19852, "title": "有几个小短片，帮你快速了解 Airbnb 这样的公司", "description": "请戳黄色链接部分观看。", "date": "2015-12-29T06:30:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 21193, "name": "发展历程"}, {"id": 1270, "name": "Airbnb"}, {"id": 2555, "name": "spotify"}, {"id": 1520, "name": "Uber"}], "category": 18, "author": 378446, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 104, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702124333CygPA4jNubWTv83d.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tTelegraph为 <span><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/technology-video/12021531/the-history-of-airbnb.html\" target=\"_blank\">Airbnb</a></span>、<span><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/technology-video/12033877/the-history-of-spotify.html\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify </a></span>等公司各制作了两分钟左右的视频短片，简明地介绍了这些公司的发展历程，和一些年度大事记。你可以点击黄色的链接部分观看这些视频。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这些小短片按照时间顺序，梳理了这些科技公司的创始年份、融资情况、成功营销案例以及新功能上线的过程等，能够让观众在短时间内清晰明了地了解到它们的发展历程。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/technology-video/12021531/the-history-of-airbnb.html\" target=\"_blank\">Airbnb</a></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021243326gF5P7D9QBWkRKd2.jpg\" width=\"616\" height=\"350\" title=\"视频截图\" alt=\"视频截图\" data-ratio=\"0.56818182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021243321nEVfdYRpW4AzIv0.jpg\" width=\"616\" height=\"344\" title=\"视频截图\" alt=\"视频截图\" data-ratio=\"0.55844156\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>视频截图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t创立于 <span>2008 </span>年，<span>Airbnb </span>起初是三个年轻人无力支付房租，为了把自己的屋子租出去而创立的简单网站。<span>Airbnb</span>是 <span>AirBed and Breakfast </span>的缩写，名为“空中食宿”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2011</span>年是见证 <span>Airbnb </span>高速发展的一年，这一年里 <span>Airbnb </span>的服务难以置信地增长了 <span>800%，</span>来自 <span>89 </span>个国家的人们为租客们敞开家门，提供短期住宿。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2012</span>年， <span>Airbnb </span>上线了手机 <span>APP</span>，当时已经有 <span>100 </span>万用户及 <span>12 </span>万住所供客人选择。<span>2014</span>年，<span>Airbnb </span>已经拥有 <span>1</span>千万用户及 <span>55 </span>万住所。到今年，<span>Airbnb</span>的估值达到 <span>250 </span>亿美元，用户增长至 <span>6</span>千万。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/technology-video/12033877/the-history-of-spotify.html\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124333P1VidxnybfX8QqOg.jpg\" title=\"视频截图\" alt=\"视频截图\" data-ratio=\"0.56219709\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t与 <span>AirBnb </span>一样，<span>Spotify </span>也是迅速发展中的科技公司。<span>Spotify </span>是全球最大的流媒体音乐服务平台， <span>2006 </span>年在瑞典成立， <span>2008 </span>年正式上线。在 <span>2008 </span>年及 <span>2011 </span>年成功融资之后， <span>Spotify </span>在 <span>2011 </span>年的付费用户人数达到 <span>100 </span>万，同时与 <span>Facebook </span>合作推出社交音乐服务，允许用户直接通过 <span>Facebook </span>收听音乐，并即时获得好友收听音乐的信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2012</span>年， <span>Spotify </span>已有 <span>400 万</span>付费用户。<span>2015</span>年 <span>Spotify </span>推出创新服务：能够根据用户的跑步节奏智能匹配歌曲。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t除了上述介绍的公司，<span>Telegraph </span>还为 <span><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/uber/11962859/The-history-of-Uber.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uber</a></span>、<span><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/apple/11654355/The-history-of-Apple.html\" target=\"_blank\">Apple</a>, <a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/google/11984555/Rise-of-a-tech-giant-the-history-of-Google.html\" target=\"_blank\">Google </a></span>等公司制作了发展历程的介绍视频，方便用户们快速了解这些知名公司的发展历程，你可以戳进黄色的链接观看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来自Google\r\n</p>\n\n"}